  ## What is CENTAUR LANG?
  CENTAUR LANG is the world's first Human+AI programming language.
  It transforms natural language into production-ready code.
  
  ## Who created it?
  CENTAUR LANG was created by Chris Conen (Human) and Claude (AI)
  as part of the CENTAUR partnership.
  
